"use strict";(self.webpackChunkexonumia_cc=self.webpackChunkexonumia_cc||[]).push([[52541],{47074:(a,n,i)=>{i.r(n),i.d(n,{data:()=>e});const e={key:"v-14307907",path:"/zaf/ts/bitcoin-is-like-sports/",title:"Bitcoin Yi Fana na Mintlangu",lang:"ts",frontmatter:{translators:[{name:"Tirhani Mabasa",href:"https://twitter.com/TirhaniMabasa"}]},excerpt:"",headers:[],filePathRelative:"zaf/ts/bitcoin-is-like-sports/README.md",git:{updatedTime:1761164621e3}}},63953:(a,n,i)=>{i.r(n),i.d(n,{default:()=>h});var e=i(66252);const u=(0,e._)("h1",{id:"bitcoin-yi-fana-na-mintlangu",tabindex:"-1"},[(0,e._)("a",{class:"header-anchor",href:"#bitcoin-yi-fana-na-mintlangu","aria-hidden":"true"},"#"),(0,e.Uk)(" Bitcoin Yi Fana na Mintlangu")],-1),t=(0,e.Uk)("hi @thebitcoinrabbi "),l={href:"https://twitter.com/thebitcoinrabbi/status/1349445548500262916",target:"_blank",rel:"noopener noreferrer"},k=(0,e.Uk)("2021/01/13"),o=(0,e.uE)("<p>Ndzi hlamuserile minkarhi yo hlaya leswaku #bitcoin yi tirha njhani naswona yi le ndzhawu yin’we ku fana na ntlangu wa swa mintlangu. Ndzi vona swi pfuna ku hlamula swivutiso leswi talaka ku vutisiwa:</p><p>Q: Xana i mani a nga tumbuluxa beyisibolo?<br> A: A swi na nkoka. Munhu wun’wana na wun’wana laha misaveni a nga tlanga. A swi na mhaka ku mutumbuluxi wo sungula a lava ku cinca milawu kumbe ku ti hakela tipoyinti kumbe swin’wana. A hi na mhaka ya leswaku u ehleketa yini hi ntlangu wa hina.</p><p>Q: Xana i mani murhangeri wa ntlangu?<br> A: A ku na murhangeri, hinkwerhu hi lo hleketa ku tlanga. Hinkwerhu ha yi tiva milawu na ku yi landzelela, naswona loko wun’wana a kanganyisa wun’wana, va humesiwa eka ntlangu. Loko munhu a tihakela tipoyinti leti a nga riki na tona, a hi n’wi tekeli enhlokweni.</p><p>Q: Xana hi swi tiva njhani leswaku milawu a yi nge cinci?<br> A: Hinkwerhi hi pfumelelanile na yona loko hi sungula ku tlanga, naswona loyi a tsakelaka ku ya emahlweni a tlanga na milawu leyi u ta endla tano, naswona loko va cinca, va nga hlawula ku ya langa kun’wana.</p><p>Q: A yi nge hekiwi kee?<br> A: Hinkwaswo swi le rivaleni eka mani na mani. Hinkwerhu hi nga vona rivala hinkwaro na minkutlunya. Loko ku ri na yoyi a yivelaka, hinkwerhu ha swi tiva leswaku va lahlekile.</p><p>Q: Hikokwalahokayini wu ri na nkoka?<br> A: Hinkwerhu hi ehlekete ku tlanga, kutani i wa nkoka eka hina. Loko wun’wana a tsakela ku hi joyina, u fanele ku pfumelelana ku amukela tipoyinti ta hina na nkoka.</p><p>Ndzi vona wu ri na nkoka, kutani i ya nkoka. Nkoka wu teka thlelo ro karhi.</p><p>Q: Xana a yi nge yirisiwi?<br> A: Kumbexana, kambe vanhu va ya emahlweni va tlanga hi tinhonga na bolo, ku nga twisiwi van’wana ku vava, kutani mfumo wu ga wu yimisa ku tlangiwa, kambe wu nga alela leswaku wu tlangiwa, kambe a va nge yirisi khonsepe ya ku ba bolo hi nhonga, ntlangu wu ta ya emahlweni kun’wana.</p><p>Q: Xana ndzi nga joyina?<br> A: Endla leswi u swi lavaka. Ndzi le ku tiphineni hi ntlangu wa beyisibolo, u nga joyina kumbe u nga HFSP.</p>",9),w={},h=(0,i(83744).Z)(w,[["render",function(a,n){const i=(0,e.up)("OutboundLink"),w=(0,e.up)("LanguageDropdown");return(0,e.wg)(),(0,e.iD)(e.HY,null,[u,(0,e._)("p",null,[t,(0,e._)("a",l,[k,(0,e.Wm)(i)])]),(0,e.Wm)(w),o],64)}]])},83744:(a,n)=>{n.Z=(a,n)=>{const i=a.__vccOpts||a;for(const[a,e]of n)i[a]=e;return i}}}]);